high_descs: Turn left, walk into the bedroom, turn left, walk forward, and then stand in front of the fridge.
Open the cabinet, pick up the knife, and close the cabinet door.
Turn around and face the bread on the white table.
Slice up the bread with the knife.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the knife on the shelf, and then close the door.
Turn around and face the white diningtable.
Pick up a slice of bread from the bread basket.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Open the cabinet door, place a slice of bread on the shelf, and then close the door.
Pick up another slice of bread from the countertop.
Drop the bread on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Slice up the bread placing the items in the black cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left to head to the bedroom and turn left to reach the fridge across the passage.
Pick up the knife from the fridge.
Turn around to reach the bread on the table.
Cut the bread into slices with the knife.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn around to reach the diningtable.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Cool the slice of bread in the fridge and take the bread out.
Head right to reach the countertop next to the microwave.
Put the slice of bread on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled Bread on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take the knife from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go near the bread.
Cut the bread into slices using the knife.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the knife into the fridge.
Then turn around and go near the diningtable.
Take the bread from the table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the bread into the refrigerator.
Then take it out and go near the oven countertop.
Put the slice of bread into the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Cut the bread into slices using the knife on the CounterTop.
